Attack type: none

Powerful large crossbow.
While bows require both hands, a crossbow is
held in one, but arming each bolt takes time.

Equip bolts to use.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of bolt.
Name: 雷のヘビークロスボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
The Katana is drawn from the scabbard at
lightning speed, using an Iaijutsu technique.

Iaijutsu allows the wielder to charge
forward to swiftly cut down distant foes.
Name: 雷の居合い刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Thick iron shield of Shiva of the East.
Heaviest of the standard shields.
Deflects enemy attacks. A famous specimen
from Shiva's collection, but none who have
faced it have lived to tell the tale.
Name: 雷の鉄の円盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash

This wide single-edged shortsword is
the favorite of lowly thieves and bandits.

Primarily a slicing weapon, but highly
effective when used for critical hits,
such as after parrying or from behind.
Name: 雷の短刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

This medium metal shield is elegantly
carved and painted.
Although it is thought to have been used by
ancient knights of the nobility, its defense
capabilities are similar to other shields.
Name: 雷のナイトシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Great Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Large wooden club.

The giant Undead of Blighttown wield these
clubs, which became poisonous from the
influence of their surroundings.
Name: 雷の蛮兵クラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round leather-covered shield.
A standard, widely-used shield.

Small shields are always less stable, but
landing critical hits after parry is easier.
Name: 雷のレザーシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Crossbow
Attack type: none

Standard crossbow issued to soldiers.
While bows require both hands, a crossbow is
held in one, but arming each bolt takes time.

Equip bolts to use.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of bolt.
Name: 雷のライトクロスボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Large bow. Projectile weapon for experienced
hunters. Equip arrows to use.

Hold bow and press <?platmsg@10002?> to aim.
Aim for heads of humanoid foes.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of arrows.
Name: 雷のロングボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Widely-used standard straight sword, only
matched in ubiquity by the shortsword.

An accessible sword which inflicts consistent
regular damage and high slash damage, making
it applicable to a variety of situations.
Name: 雷のロングソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Thrust

Halberd with a large, hard beak-like
protrusion. Inflicts thrust damage.
Instead of thrusting like a spear, the
wielder of the Lucerne aims to club
the head with its hard beak.
Name: 雷のルッツエルン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Iron hammer with a protrusive pommel.
Standard weapon for clerics.
This simple bladeless strike weapon is
effective against most foes, and can
break the guard of a shield. However,
one miss leaves one wide open.
Name: 雷のメイス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

Standard small thrusting sword.
Unsharpened but pointed solid
shaft can pierce tough armor.

Can be thrust using the weight of one's body,
and is very effective for critical attacks.
Name: 雷のメイル・ブレイカー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Hammer with sharp spikes on its pommel.
One of the more barbaric cleric weapons.

The effect of these spikes makes this
strike-based weapon also cause bleeding.
Name: 雷のモーニングスター

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

Giant curved sword forged using special
methods in an Eastern land.
This unparalleled weapon cuts like a Katana
but is heavier than a Nata machete.
Requires extreme strength, dexterity,
and stamina to wield.
Name: 雷の大曲刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Whip
Attack type: Regular

Whip with sharp spikes.

Only slightly effective against armor and
tough scales, but quite formidable against
enemies with exposed skin.
Also causes heavy bleeding.
Name: 雷のスパイクウィップ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

This dagger is useful after parrying and is
normally equipped in the left hand.

A favorite of the knights of Carim, who are
famous for fighting without a shield.
Name: 雷のパリングダガー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Spear with blade attached to broad point.
Boasts long reach, and can slice.

The wide range of this spear makes it
adaptable to many situations. Its strength
lies in its length, but in cramped quarters,
this backfires, and slices ricochet off walls.
Name: 雷のパルチザン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Thrust

Traditionally a mining tool, but the hard
cone on the pommel is effective in battle.

A downward swing of the Pickaxe can crush
stone; a human head would be an afterthought.
Name: 雷のつるはし

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Thrust

Shield of certain knights of Catarina, used
in attacks with a large protrusion in center.

Can be used as a thrust weapon.
Name: 雷のピアスシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Long Spear
Attack type: Thrust

Long spear with a very long red hilt.
Traditionally used by groups of soldiers.
Specially designed for distance thrusting.
Has the longest range of the non-projectile
weapons, but its very length makes it
somewhat difficult to handle.
Name: 雷のパイク

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Makeshift shield built from wood planks.
Provides minimal protection,
but at a cost of moderate humiliation.
Name: 雷の木板の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round wooden shield crafted in Lordran
featuring an impressive red and white design.
The giant trees in Lordran are distant
offspring of the great stone archtrees.
This shield inherits their properties, and
the wood greatly reduces magic damage.
Name: 雷のラウンドシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

Standard thrusting sword. Regular one-handed
attack can be delivered with shield held up.
Can parry with use of left hand.

Thrusting attacks pierce and are effective
against foes with hard exteriors, but the
wielder is left open to damage after a swing.
Name: 雷のレイピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

A club with leather nailed to the pommel.
The burg Undead merchant proudly peddles
this club, but its reinforcement is shoddy.
Indeed, its attack is stronger, but the
club is no longer dependably sturdy.
Name: 雷の強化クラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

A rapier with intricate decorations. Chosen
weapon of the infamous Undead Prince Ricard.
Ricard's exploits are told in a monomyth.
He was born into royalty, but wandered the
lands in a fateful ill-conceived journey.
He became Undead, and disappeared up North.
Name: 雷の貴族の刺剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

A legendary weapon of the Way of White,
granted to an Undead paladin long ago.

Once blessed with the protection of a white
flame, but its power has all but faded, so
that it provides only slight HP recovery.
Name: 雷のデザインコンテスト用盾Ｂ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Small curved sword. Each hit inflicts little
damage, but fluid chain attacks are deadly.

The scimitar's sharp slashing attacks are
effective against cloth and flesh, but not
against metal armor or tough scales.
Name: 雷のシミター

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Slash

Halberd with a large blade.
Scythe adjusted for battle.

Designed especially for slicing. However,
one false swing leaves one wide open.
Name: 雷のサイズ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

A curved greatsword used in a
mysterious ancient rite.

Imbued with a frightful occult energy
which restores HP with each hit.
Name: 雷のラム・ダオ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Small bow. Standard projectile weapon.
Equip arrows to use.

Hold bow and press <?platmsg@10002?> to aim.
Aim for heads of humanoid foes.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of arrows.
Name: 雷のショートボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

This small straight sword is widely used,
to an extent only matched by the longsword.

An accessible sword which inflicts consistent
regular damage and high slash damage, making
it applicable to a variety of situations.
Name: 雷のショートソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Curved sword with sharply curved blade.

Created by Arstor, Earl of Carim.
Requires great skill to wield, but evades
shield defense to sneak in damage.
Name: 雷のショーテル

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Crossbow
Attack type: none

Large crossbow with long distance used by
Carim snipers. Often used with sniper bolts.

But while crossbows are normally easy to
use, the Sniper Crossbow requires dexterity.
Name: 雷のスナイパークロス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Thrust

Standard spear used commonly by soldiers.
Long reach, and can be used with shield up.
Effective against hard exteriors, and can hit
for high damage at the right moment of an
enemy's swing. But the hit radius is small,
and it is easily blocked by shields.
Name: 雷のショートスピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Shield of the savage mountain bandits.
Uniquely-shaped with a large black spider
etched upon it.
Has resistance to poison.
Name: 雷の蜘蛛の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Shield of the infamous Darkwraith Kirk,
Knight of Thorns. Covered with spikes.

Can be used as a weapon.
Sharp spikes cause heavy bleeding.
Name: 雷のトゲの盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Shield of Solaire of Astora, Knight of
Sunlight. Decorated with a holy symbol,
but Solaire illustrated it himself, and it
has no divine powers of its own. As it turns
out, Solaire's incredible prowess is a product
of his own training, and nothing more.
Name: 雷の太陽の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Small round metal shield.
Four protrusions used to parry attacks.

Small shields are always less stable, but
landing critical hits after parry is easier.
This shield is specialized for parrying.
Name: 雷のターゲットシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Medium metal shield. Decorated with a tower,
the symbol of protection.
A standard, widely-used shield.
Name: 雷のヒーターシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatshield
Attack type: Strike

Metal greatshield. Used by Knight Berenike,
known for his heavy armor. This thick plate
of iron is heavily defensive but ultra heavy.
Greatshields are very stable, and deflect
attacks. However, one cannot parry,
and instead bashes with the shield.
Name: 雷のタワーシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
Known for its brisk slashing motions.

The Uchigatana cuts beautifully and causes
bleeding, but its blade is easily nicked.
Name: 雷の打刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Thrust

Hammer with a large beak-shaped pommel.
Originally a pickaxe; redesigned for battle.

This simple but deadly weapon hits heavily
with thrust damage, such that it easily
cracks metal armor.
Name: 雷のウォーピック

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
Very unusual specimen with a long blade.

The blade is extremely long,
but as a result, quite easily broken.
Name: 雷の名刀なんとか

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Whip
Attack type: Regular

Leather whip.
Not intended for battle.

Virtually ineffective against armor and tough
scales, but quite formidable against enemies
with exposed skin.
Name: 雷のウィップ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Thrust

A long-hilted spear with a barbed point.
Long reach, and can be used with shield up.
Effective against hard exteriors, and hits
for high damage at the right moment of an
enemy's swing. But the hit radius is small,
and it is easily blocked by shields.
Name: 雷のロングスピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Vertically elongated wooden shield.
Decorated with a white dragon.

Wood shields are lighter than metal shields,
but with lower physical damage reduction,
and reduced shield stability.
Name: 雷のラージウッドシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Ultra Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

One of the gigantic straight greatswords.

As the name suggests, the Zweihander is held
with two hands, but its wielder must still be
inhumanly strong. It is this great weight
that sends foes flying when hit solidly.
Name: 雷のツヴァイヘンダー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Catalyst
Attack type: Strike

Catalyst of Big Hat Logan, the great sorcerer
and seeker of knowledge.
Originally the same catalyst employed by the
Vinheim sorcerers, only terribly strengthened
over time due to Logan's use. Very powerful
when used by one of superior intelligence.
Name: ローガンの杖

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Large bow. Projectile weapon for experienced
hunters. Equip arrows to use.

Hold bow and press <?platmsg@10002?> to aim.
Aim for heads of humanoid foes.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of arrows.
Name: ロングボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Widely-used standard straight sword, only
matched in ubiquity by the shortsword.

An accessible sword which inflicts consistent
regular damage and high slash damage, making
it applicable to a variety of situations.
Name: ロングソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The choice weapon of the infamous Darkwraith
Kirk, also known as the Knight of Thorns for
the gnarly spikes on his favorite weapon.

The sharp spikes of this ghastly weapon
cause heavy bleeding.
Name: 雷のトゲの直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

The preferred black bow of the heroic
archer Pharis.

Has a longer range than standard bows,
but is more difficult to use. Without proper
abilities, results will be underwhelming.
Name: 雷のハンターの弓

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatshield
Attack type: Strike

Greatshield of the mighty knight Tarkus.

Built of special black iron and even heavier
than Knight Berenike's tower shield.
Especially resistant to fire attacks and
effective for shield bashing.
Name: 雷のデザインコンテスト用盾Ｄ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Half of the blade of this straight sword is
broken off.

Only the completely Hollowed would even
consider using this as a weapon.
Name: 雷の折れた直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Medium metal shield.
Decorated by an ancient blue Caduceus.
A standard, widely-used shield.
Name: 雷の兵士の青盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round wooden shield crafted in Lordran.
Decorated by an ancient blue Caduceus.
The giant trees in Lordran are distant
offspring of the great stone archtrees.
This shield inherits their properties,
and the wood greatly reduces magic damage.
Name: 雷の双蛇の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round wooden shield.
Cracked and nearly broken.

Wood shields are lighter than metal shields,
but this one has lower physical damage
reduction stability, partly due to cracking.
Name: 雷の壊れかけの盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Ultra Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

The lesser Capra demons use these greatswords
in pairs. The blade is cast iron and hooked.

The sword is imbued with no particular magic,
but for those who have the strength, its
great weight will smash foes mercilessly.
Name: 雷のデーモンの鉈

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Great Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Demon weapon built from the stone archtrees.
Used by lesser demons at North Undead Asylum.

This hammer is imbued with no special power,
but can merrily beat foes to a pulp,
providing you have the strength to wield it.
Name: 雷のデーモンの大槌

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Regular

Halberd of the gargoyle guarding the
Bell of Awakening in the Undead Church.

Perfectly standard bronze halberd
without any special power.
Name: 雷のガーゴイルの斧槍

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Old medium metal shield of unknown origin.
The grass crest is lightly imbued with magic,
which slightly speeds stamina recovery.
Name: 雷の草紋の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Metal shield wielded by Hollow soldiers.
Heavily rusted but sturdy, providing a
strong defense.
Name: 雷の兵士の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Large, leather-covered round shield.
Choice shield for hunters.

Wood shields are lighter than metal shields,
but with lower physical damage reduction,
and reduced shield stability.
Name: 雷のラージレザーシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

This single-bladed blood-stained greatsword
is the choice weapon of the slithering 
serpent men of Sen's Fortress.

An ordinary human will have great difficulty
swinging this heavy beast effectively.
Name: 雷の蛇人の大剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Curved sword of Anor Londo painting guards.
Unique shape with flat tip.
The guardians, who strike down those who
dare threaten the paintings, attack in a
continuous, circular dancing motion,
a technique passed down through generations.
Name: 雷のエレーミアスの曲剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Small, leather-covered round shield,
reinforced in critical spots with metal.

Small shields are always less stable, but
landing critical hits after parry is easier.
Name: 雷のスモールレザーシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The hilt of this lost sword was found
discarded in the Undead Asylum.

Only slightly better than one's bare hands,
and not recommended for extensive use.
Be certain to find a replacement quickly.
Name: 雷のすごく折れた直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

This standard longsword, belonging to Solaire
of Astora, is of high quality, is well-
forged, and has been kept in good repair.

Easy-to-use and dependable, but unlikely to
live up to its grandiose name.
Name: 雷の太陽騎士の直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round wooden shield crafted in Lordran.
Decorated with the ancient Labrys axe.
The giant trees in Lordran are distant
offspring of the great stone archtrees.
This shield inherits their properties, 
and the wood reduces magic damage.
Name: 雷の骸骨兵の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Thrust

Halberd with a large, hard beak-like
protrusion. Inflicts thrust damage.
Instead of thrusting like a spear, the
wielder of the Lucerne aims to club
the head with its hard beak.
Name: ルッツエルン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Iron hammer with a protrusive pommel.
Standard weapon for clerics.
This simple bladeless strike weapon is
effective against most foes, and can
break the guard of a shield. However,
one miss leaves one wide open.
Name: メイス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatshield
Attack type: Strike

Greatshield of the mighty knight Tarkus.

Built of special black iron and even heavier
than Knight Berenike's tower shield.
Especially resistant to fire attacks and
effective for shield bashing.
Name: 魔法Ａのデザインコンテスト用盾Ｄ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Crossbow
Attack type: none

Repeating crossbow cherished by the weapon
craftsman Eidas. Its elaborate design makes
it closer to a work of art than a weapon.
Intricate mechanism makes heavy damage
possible through triple-shot firing of bolts,
but in fact each bolt inflicts less damage.
Name: 魔法Ａの三連クロスボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Shield of the knights of the ancient kingdom
of Balder. Tweaked for improved stability.
Balder was the home of Knight King Rendal,
but the kingdom was reduced to ruins after
a widespread outbreak of Undead.
Name: 魔法Ａのロングシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The knights of the ancient kingdom of Balder
wielded these rock-solid, long swords which
are excellent for thrust attacks.
Balder was the home of Knight King Rendal,
but the kingdom was reduced to ruins after
a widespread outbreak of Undead.
Name: 魔法Ａの刺突直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The choice weapon of the infamous Darkwraith
Kirk, also known as the Knight of Thorns for
the gnarly spikes on his favorite weapon.

The sharp spikes of this ghastly weapon
cause heavy bleeding.
Name: 魔法Ａのトゲの直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

This standard greatsword is normally wielded
with two hands due to its great weight.

Usually swung in large arcs and effective
against multiple foes. Far from ideal when
fighting in tight quarters.
Name: 魔法Ａのバスタードソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Axe
Attack type: Regular

Standard battle axe. Inflicts regular damage,
making it effective in various situations.
Powerful attack due to its weight, but one
wrong swing leaves the wielder wide open,
so timing and proximity to the enemy must
be judged carefully.
Name: 魔法Ａのバトルアクス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

The preferred black bow of the heroic
archer Pharis.

Has a longer range than standard bows,
but is more difficult to use. Without proper
abilities, results will be underwhelming.
Name: 魔法Ａのハンターの弓

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Metal hammer of Andre of Astora,
blacksmith at the Old Church.

Can be used as a strike weapon, but better
left in the hands of its talented owner.
Name: 魔法Ａのアンドレの金槌

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

The bloodshield spoken of in the lost
legends. The red of blood is slightly
enchanted, and boosts various resistances.
Name: 魔法Ａのデザインコンテスト用盾Ｃ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatshield
Attack type: Strike

Giant wooden wheel encircled by spikes.
Half-melded to a strange skeleton.

Can be used as a greatshield, only for the
great gaps. But at least the spikes turn into
weapons with a good spin. Strange indeed!
Name: 魔法Ａの車輪の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular

The wide blade of this straight sword
emphasizes slicing and has no thrust attack.

The horizontal sweeping motion makes this
sword effective against multiple enemies.
Name: 魔法Ａのブロードソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Half of the blade of this straight sword is
broken off.

Only the completely Hollowed would even
consider using this as a weapon.
Name: 魔法Ａの折れた直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Very small round metal shield.
Parry attacks with large center protrusion.

Small shields are always less stable, but
landing critical hits after parry is easier.
This shield is specialized for parrying.
Name: 魔法Ａのバックラー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Axe
Attack type: Regular

Giant butcher knife wielded by the Undead
man-eating cook lurking in the Depths.
More a tool for subduing and preparing live
catches than an actual weapon. Those who
have faced this deadly blade have a deeper
sense of how helpless prey must feel.
Name: 魔法Ａの大包丁

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Medium metal shield.
Decorated by an ancient blue Caduceus.
A standard, widely-used shield.
Name: 魔法Ａの兵士の青盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round wooden shield crafted in Lordran.
Decorated by an ancient blue Caduceus.
The giant trees in Lordran are distant
offspring of the great stone archtrees.
This shield inherits their properties,
and the wood greatly reduces magic damage.
Name: 魔法Ａの双蛇の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Fists
Attack type: Strike

The weapon augments one's bare hands
with thick, studded leather.

The Caestus has a short reach, but quick
cool down. Amount of damage inflicted is
dependent on its wearer's strength.
Name: 魔法Ａのセスタス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Fists
Attack type: Slash

A weapon formed by three sharp claws.

Attacks cause bleeding, and the wounds
inflicted are not easily mended. Preferred
weapon of the spooks of an Eastern land.
Name: 魔法Ａのかぎ爪

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

This larger type of greatsword is normally
wielded with two hands due to its weight.

This highly flexible greatsword can be used
to attack in swings or thrusts.
Name: 魔法Ａのクレイモア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

A simple wooden club.
This simple bladeless strike weapon is
effective against most foes, is easily
handled, and can break the guard of a shield.
However, a single miss makes one wide open,
so timing and proximities are crucial.
Name: 魔法Ａのクラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Composite bow emphasizing power.
Requires more strength than standard bows.

However, its range is shorter, making it
unfit for sniping.
Name: 魔法Ａのコンポジットボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round wooden shield.
Cracked and nearly broken.

Wood shields are lighter than metal shields,
but this one has lower physical damage
reduction stability, partly due to cracking.
Name: 魔法Ａの壊れかけの盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

This standard small dagger has only a modest
attack but can be jabbed in rapid succession,
and is effective in critical hits such as
after a parry or when stabbing in the back.
With both slash and thrust attacks, this
dagger is useful in various situations.
Name: 魔法Ａのダガー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular

The sword of the knights of the Four Kings of
New Londo. Its blade is wide and thick, and
it is wielded in an unusual manner.
When the Four Kings were seduced by evil,
their knights became Darkwraiths, servants
of the Dark who wielded these darkswords.
Name: 魔法Ａのダークソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Ultra Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

The lesser Capra demons use these greatswords
in pairs. The blade is cast iron and hooked.

The sword is imbued with no particular magic,
but for those who have the strength, its
great weight will smash foes mercilessly.
Name: 魔法Ａのデーモンの鉈

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Great Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Demon weapon built from the stone archtrees.
Used by lesser demons at North Undead Asylum.

This hammer is imbued with no special power,
but can merrily beat foes to a pulp,
providing you have the strength to wield it.
Name: 魔法Ａのデーモンの大槌

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greataxe
Attack type: Regular

Carved from the bones of fellow demons.
Wielded by the lesser Taurus demons.

This axe is imbued with no special power,
but can merrily beat foes to a pulp,
providing you have the strength to wield it.
Name: 魔法Ａのデーモンの大斧

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatshield
Attack type: Strike

Greatshield with an eagle design. Lightest
and easiest greatshield to handle.

Greatshields are very stable, and deflect
attacks. But one cannot parry, and instead
bashes with the shield.
Name: 魔法Ａの大鷲の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Wooden shield.
Decorated with the ancient symbol of
a double-headed eagle, painted yellow.

Wood shields are lighter than metal shields,
but with lower physical damage reduction,
and reduced shield stability.
Name: 魔法Ａのウッドシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Frightful occult shield. Defends against
divine weapons and lightning.

In an ill-fated plot to destroy the very
gods, the followers of the occult once
attempted to steal the power of
Gravelord Nito, the first of the dead.
Name: 魔法Ａのデザインコンテスト用盾Ａ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The largest of the thrusting swords.
Can pierce an armored knight in one thrust.

The blade is also sharp,
allowing slicing as well.
Name: 魔法Ａのエストック

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Small curved sword. Each hit inflicts little
damage, but fluid chain attacks are deadly.

The falchion's sharp slashing attacks are
effective against cloth and flesh, but not
against metal armor or tough scales.
Name: 魔法Ａのファルシオン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

This greatsword with an undulating blade is
the choice weapon of the slithering serpent
men of Sen's Fortress.

This weapon is designed to flay the skin and
causes heavy bleeding.
Name: 魔法Ａのフランベルジェ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Axe
Attack type: Regular

Sliced tail of the gargoyle guarding the
Bell of Awakening in the Undead Church.

Can be used as a bronze battle axe.
Bends dramatically during large attacks,
owing to its nature as a tail.
Name: 魔法Ａのガーゴイルの尾斧

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Regular

Halberd of the gargoyle guarding the
Bell of Awakening in the Undead Church.

Perfectly standard bronze halberd
without any special power.
Name: 魔法Ａのガーゴイルの斧槍

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Bronze shield of the gargoyle guarding the
Bell of Awakening in the Undead Church.
The gargoyle's skin is tough by itself, and
perhaps its shield may have been a prop,
for it is a rare example of a metal shield
that does not reduce physical damage 100%.
Name: 魔法Ａのガーゴイルの盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatshield
Attack type: Strike

Greatshield made of bronze and marcasite.
Used by giant sentinels of Anor Londo.
Marcasite, or white iron, is effective
against non-physical damage, but as the
shield is designed for the giant sentinels,
its weight is unbearable.
Name: 魔法Ａの巨人の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Old medium metal shield of unknown origin.
The grass crest is lightly imbued with magic,
which slightly speeds stamina recovery.
Name: 魔法Ａの草紋の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Great Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Giant tree branch serves as a wooden club.
Smashes enemies from upside the head.

The leaping attack is a trademark of clubs,
and this giant club is no exception.
Name: 魔法Ａのグレートクラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Slash

Weapon with a long curved blade. Converted
from a wheat-harvesting tool.

The magnificent sharp curved blade
instills fear in opponents. Perhaps it is
their survival instinct at work.
Name: 魔法Ａの鎌

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greataxe
Attack type: Regular

This greataxe is a veritable mass of iron.
Its weight sends foes flying, but makes it
difficult to handle without inhuman strength.

Any miss makes one very vulnerable, as each
swing requires the full force of the body.
Name: 魔法Ａのグレートアクス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Ultra Greatsword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

One of the gigantic straight greatswords.

Very few have what it takes to wield this
incredibly heavy, damage-dealing monster.
A favorite of the Knights Berenike, known for
their heavy armor, and Black Iron Tarkus.
Name: 魔法Ａのグレートソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Long-hilted weapon mixing spear and axe is
difficult to handle, requiring both strength
and dexterity. The Halberd has two elementary
attacks: spear-like thrusting and large
sweeping swings. However, one false swing
and the wielder is left wide open.
Name: 魔法Ａのハルバード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Axe
Attack type: Regular

Small hand axe. Appears identical to a
lumberjack's tool, but has an ideal weight
and strength, and is easy to handle.
One wrong swing leaves the wielder wide
open, so timing and proximity to the enemy
must be judged carefully.
Name: 魔法Ａのハンドアクス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Small metal shield.
A standard, widely-used shield.

This shield is easy to use, and is one of
the smallest shields that offers
100% physical damage reduction.
Name: 魔法Ａのカイトシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Crossbow
Attack type: none

Powerful large crossbow.
While bows require both hands, a crossbow is
held in one, but arming each bolt takes time.

Equip bolts to use.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of bolt.
Name: 魔法Ａのヘビークロスボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Metal shield wielded by Hollow soldiers.
Heavily rusted but sturdy, providing a
strong defense.
Name: 魔法Ａの兵士の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
The Katana is drawn from the scabbard at
lightning speed, using an Iaijutsu technique.

Iaijutsu allows the wielder to charge
forward to swiftly cut down distant foes.
Name: 魔法Ａの居合い刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Thick iron shield of Shiva of the East.
Heaviest of the standard shields.
Deflects enemy attacks. A famous specimen
from Shiva's collection, but none who have
faced it have lived to tell the tale.
Name: 魔法Ａの鉄の円盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash

This wide single-edged shortsword is
the favorite of lowly thieves and bandits.

Primarily a slicing weapon, but highly
effective when used for critical hits,
such as after parrying or from behind.
Name: 魔法Ａの短刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

This medium metal shield is elegantly
carved and painted.
Although it is thought to have been used by
ancient knights of the nobility, its defense
capabilities are similar to other shields.
Name: 魔法Ａのナイトシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Great Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Large wooden club.

The giant Undead of Blighttown wield these
clubs, which became poisonous from the
influence of their surroundings.
Name: 魔法Ａの蛮兵クラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Large, leather-covered round shield.
Choice shield for hunters.

Wood shields are lighter than metal shields,
but with lower physical damage reduction,
and reduced shield stability.
Name: 魔法Ａのラージレザーシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round leather-covered shield.
A standard, widely-used shield.

Small shields are always less stable, but
landing critical hits after parry is easier.
Name: 魔法Ａのレザーシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Crossbow
Attack type: none

Standard crossbow issued to soldiers.
While bows require both hands, a crossbow is
held in one, but arming each bolt takes time.

Equip bolts to use.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of bolt.
Name: 魔法Ａのライトクロスボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Large bow. Projectile weapon for experienced
hunters. Equip arrows to use.

Hold bow and press <?platmsg@10002?> to aim.
Aim for heads of humanoid foes.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of arrows.
Name: 魔法Ａのロングボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Widely-used standard straight sword, only
matched in ubiquity by the shortsword.

An accessible sword which inflicts consistent
regular damage and high slash damage, making
it applicable to a variety of situations.
Name: 魔法Ａのロングソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Thrust

Halberd with a large, hard beak-like
protrusion. Inflicts thrust damage.
Instead of thrusting like a spear, the
wielder of the Lucerne aims to club
the head with its hard beak.
Name: 魔法Ａのルッツエルン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Iron hammer with a protrusive pommel.
Standard weapon for clerics.
This simple bladeless strike weapon is
effective against most foes, and can
break the guard of a shield. However,
one miss leaves one wide open.
Name: 魔法Ａのメイス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

Standard small thrusting sword.
Unsharpened but pointed solid
shaft can pierce tough armor.

Can be thrust using the weight of one's body,
and is very effective for critical attacks.
Name: 魔法Ａのメイル・ブレイカー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

This single-bladed blood-stained greatsword
is the choice weapon of the slithering 
serpent men of Sen's Fortress.

An ordinary human will have great difficulty
swinging this heavy beast effectively.
Name: 魔法Ａの蛇人の大剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Hammer with sharp spikes on its pommel.
One of the more barbaric cleric weapons.

The effect of these spikes makes this
strike-based weapon also cause bleeding.
Name: 魔法Ａのモーニングスター

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

Giant curved sword forged using special
methods in an Eastern land.
This unparalleled weapon cuts like a Katana
but is heavier than a Nata machete.
Requires extreme strength, dexterity,
and stamina to wield.
Name: 魔法Ａの大曲刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Whip
Attack type: Regular

Whip with sharp spikes.

Only slightly effective against armor and
tough scales, but quite formidable against
enemies with exposed skin.
Also causes heavy bleeding.
Name: 魔法Ａのスパイクウィップ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

This dagger is useful after parrying and is
normally equipped in the left hand.

A favorite of the knights of Carim, who are
famous for fighting without a shield.
Name: 魔法Ａのパリングダガー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Spear with blade attached to broad point.
Boasts long reach, and can slice.

The wide range of this spear makes it
adaptable to many situations. Its strength
lies in its length, but in cramped quarters,
this backfires, and slices ricochet off walls.
Name: 魔法Ａのパルチザン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Thrust

Traditionally a mining tool, but the hard
cone on the pommel is effective in battle.

A downward swing of the Pickaxe can crush
stone; a human head would be an afterthought.
Name: 魔法Ａのつるはし

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Thrust

Shield of certain knights of Catarina, used
in attacks with a large protrusion in center.

Can be used as a thrust weapon.
Name: 魔法Ａのピアスシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Long Spear
Attack type: Thrust

Long spear with a very long red hilt.
Traditionally used by groups of soldiers.
Specially designed for distance thrusting.
Has the longest range of the non-projectile
weapons, but its very length makes it
somewhat difficult to handle.
Name: 魔法Ａのパイク

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Makeshift shield built from wood planks.
Provides minimal protection,
but at a cost of moderate humiliation.
Name: 魔法Ａの木板の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Curved sword of Anor Londo painting guards.
Unique shape with flat tip.
The guardians, who strike down those who
dare threaten the paintings, attack in a
continuous, circular dancing motion,
a technique passed down through generations.
Name: 魔法Ａのエレーミアスの曲剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round wooden shield crafted in Lordran
featuring an impressive red and white design.
The giant trees in Lordran are distant
offspring of the great stone archtrees.
This shield inherits their properties, and
the wood greatly reduces magic damage.
Name: 魔法Ａのラウンドシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

Standard thrusting sword. Regular one-handed
attack can be delivered with shield held up.
Can parry with use of left hand.

Thrusting attacks pierce and are effective
against foes with hard exteriors, but the
wielder is left open to damage after a swing.
Name: 魔法Ａのレイピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

A club with leather nailed to the pommel.
The burg Undead merchant proudly peddles
this club, but its reinforcement is shoddy.
Indeed, its attack is stronger, but the
club is no longer dependably sturdy.
Name: 魔法Ａの強化クラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

A rapier with intricate decorations. Chosen
weapon of the infamous Undead Prince Ricard.
Ricard's exploits are told in a monomyth.
He was born into royalty, but wandered the
lands in a fateful ill-conceived journey.
He became Undead, and disappeared up North.
Name: 魔法Ａの貴族の刺剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

A legendary weapon of the Way of White,
granted to an Undead paladin long ago.

Once blessed with the protection of a white
flame, but its power has all but faded, so
that it provides only slight HP recovery.
Name: 魔法Ａのデザインコンテスト用盾Ｂ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Small curved sword. Each hit inflicts little
damage, but fluid chain attacks are deadly.

The scimitar's sharp slashing attacks are
effective against cloth and flesh, but not
against metal armor or tough scales.
Name: 魔法Ａのシミター

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Slash

Halberd with a large blade.
Scythe adjusted for battle.

Designed especially for slicing. However,
one false swing leaves one wide open.
Name: 魔法Ａのサイズ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

A curved greatsword used in a
mysterious ancient rite.

Imbued with a frightful occult energy
which restores HP with each hit.
Name: 魔法Ａのラム・ダオ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Small bow. Standard projectile weapon.
Equip arrows to use.

Hold bow and press <?platmsg@10002?> to aim.
Aim for heads of humanoid foes.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of arrows.
Name: 魔法Ａのショートボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

This small straight sword is widely used,
to an extent only matched by the longsword.

An accessible sword which inflicts consistent
regular damage and high slash damage, making
it applicable to a variety of situations.
Name: 魔法Ａのショートソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Curved sword with sharply curved blade.

Created by Arstor, Earl of Carim.
Requires great skill to wield, but evades
shield defense to sneak in damage.
Name: 魔法Ａのショーテル

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Small, leather-covered round shield,
reinforced in critical spots with metal.

Small shields are always less stable, but
landing critical hits after parry is easier.
Name: 魔法Ａのスモールレザーシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Crossbow
Attack type: none

Large crossbow with long distance used by
Carim snipers. Often used with sniper bolts.

But while crossbows are normally easy to
use, the Sniper Crossbow requires dexterity.
Name: 魔法Ａのスナイパークロス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Thrust

Standard spear used commonly by soldiers.
Long reach, and can be used with shield up.
Effective against hard exteriors, and can hit
for high damage at the right moment of an
enemy's swing. But the hit radius is small,
and it is easily blocked by shields.
Name: 魔法Ａのショートスピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Shield of the savage mountain bandits.
Uniquely-shaped with a large black spider
etched upon it.
Has resistance to poison.
Name: 魔法Ａの蜘蛛の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Shield of the infamous Darkwraith Kirk,
Knight of Thorns. Covered with spikes.

Can be used as a weapon.
Sharp spikes cause heavy bleeding.
Name: 魔法Ａのトゲの盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The hilt of this lost sword was found
discarded in the Undead Asylum.

Only slightly better than one's bare hands,
and not recommended for extensive use.
Be certain to find a replacement quickly.
Name: 魔法Ａのすごく折れた直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Shield of Solaire of Astora, Knight of
Sunlight. Decorated with a holy symbol,
but Solaire illustrated it himself, and it
has no divine powers of its own. As it turns
out, Solaire's incredible prowess is a product
of his own training, and nothing more.
Name: 魔法Ａの太陽の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

This standard longsword, belonging to Solaire
of Astora, is of high quality, is well-
forged, and has been kept in good repair.

Easy-to-use and dependable, but unlikely to
live up to its grandiose name.
Name: 魔法Ａの太陽騎士の直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Small round metal shield.
Four protrusions used to parry attacks.

Small shields are always less stable, but
landing critical hits after parry is easier.
This shield is specialized for parrying.
Name: 魔法Ａのターゲットシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Medium metal shield. Decorated with a tower,
the symbol of protection.
A standard, widely-used shield.
Name: 魔法Ａのヒーターシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatshield
Attack type: Strike

Metal greatshield. Used by Knight Berenike,
known for his heavy armor. This thick plate
of iron is heavily defensive but ultra heavy.
Greatshields are very stable, and deflect
attacks. However, one cannot parry,
and instead bashes with the shield.
Name: 魔法Ａのタワーシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
Known for its brisk slashing motions.

The Uchigatana cuts beautifully and causes
bleeding, but its blade is easily nicked.
Name: 魔法Ａの打刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Thrust

Hammer with a large beak-shaped pommel.
Originally a pickaxe; redesigned for battle.

This simple but deadly weapon hits heavily
with thrust damage, such that it easily
cracks metal armor.
Name: 魔法Ａのウォーピック

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Round wooden shield crafted in Lordran.
Decorated with the ancient Labrys axe.
The giant trees in Lordran are distant
offspring of the great stone archtrees.
This shield inherits their properties, 
and the wood reduces magic damage.
Name: 魔法Ａの骸骨兵の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
Very unusual specimen with a long blade.

The blade is extremely long,
but as a result, quite easily broken.
Name: 魔法Ａの名刀なんとか

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Whip
Attack type: Regular

Leather whip.
Not intended for battle.

Virtually ineffective against armor and tough
scales, but quite formidable against enemies
with exposed skin.
Name: 魔法Ａのウィップ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Thrust

A long-hilted spear with a barbed point.
Long reach, and can be used with shield up.
Effective against hard exteriors, and hits
for high damage at the right moment of an
enemy's swing. But the hit radius is small,
and it is easily blocked by shields.
Name: 魔法Ａのロングスピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Strike

Vertically elongated wooden shield.
Decorated with a white dragon.

Wood shields are lighter than metal shields,
but with lower physical damage reduction,
and reduced shield stability.
Name: 魔法Ａのラージウッドシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Ultra Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

One of the gigantic straight greatswords.

As the name suggests, the Zweihander is held
with two hands, but its wielder must still be
inhumanly strong. It is this great weight
that sends foes flying when hit solidly.
Name: 魔法Ａのツヴァイヘンダー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

Standard small thrusting sword.
Unsharpened but pointed solid
shaft can pierce tough armor.

Can be thrust using the weight of one's body,
and is very effective for critical attacks.
Name: メイル・ブレイカー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

This single-bladed blood-stained greatsword
is the choice weapon of the slithering 
serpent men of Sen's Fortress.

An ordinary human will have great difficulty
swinging this heavy beast effectively.
Name: 蛇人の大剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Arrow
Attack type: Thrust

Arrow granted to those bound by
Covenant to the Dark Sun Gwyndolin,
Lord Gwyn's lastborn.
Moonlight Arrows glow silver,
and inflict magic damage.
Name: 月光矢

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Thrust

Weapon born from the mystical creature of
the Darkroot Garden, the Moonlight Butterfly.

The horns of the butterfly, a being created
by Seath, are imbued with a pure magic power.
Name: カゲロウ竜の槍＜←メイルブレイカー＞

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

This sword, one of the rare dragon weapons,
came from the tail of Seath the Scaleless,
the pale white dragon who betrayed his own.
Seath is the grandfather of sorcery, and this
sword is imbued with his magic, which shall
be unleashed as a wave of moonlight.
Name: ムーンライトソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Thrust

Hammer with a sharp spike on its pommel.
One of the more barbaric cleric weapons.

Uniquely, this hammer inflicts thrust damage,
and causes bleeding.
Name: モーニングスター

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

Giant curved sword forged using special
methods in an Eastern land.
This unparalleled weapon cuts like a Katana
but is heavier than a Nata machete.
Requires extreme strength, dexterity,
and stamina to wield.
Name: 大曲刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Whip
Attack type: Regular

Whip with sharp spikes.

Only slightly effective against armor and
tough scales, but quite formidable against
enemies with exposed skin.
Also causes heavy bleeding.
Name: スパイクウィップ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The choice weapon of the infamous Darkwraith
Kirk, also known as the Knight of Thorns for
the gnarly spikes on his favorite weapon.

The sharp spikes of this ghastly weapon
cause heavy bleeding.
Name: 暗黒のトゲの直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Half of the blade of this straight sword is
broken off.

Only the completely Hollowed would even
consider using this as a weapon.
Name: 暗黒の折れた直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Great Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Demon weapon built from the stone archtrees.
Used by lesser demons at North Undead Asylum.

This hammer is imbued with no special power,
but can merrily beat foes to a pulp,
providing you have the strength to wield it.
Name: 暗黒のデーモンの大槌

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

This single-bladed blood-stained greatsword
is the choice weapon of the slithering 
serpent men of Sen's Fortress.

An ordinary human will have great difficulty
swinging this heavy beast effectively.
Name: 暗黒の蛇人の大剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Curved sword of Anor Londo painting guards.
Unique shape with flat tip.
The guardians, who strike down those who
dare threaten the paintings, attack in a
continuous, circular dancing motion,
a technique passed down through generations.
Name: 暗黒のエレーミアスの曲剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

This standard longsword, belonging to Solaire
of Astora, is of high quality, is well-
forged, and has been kept in good repair.

Easy-to-use and dependable, but unlikely to
live up to its grandiose name.
Name: 暗黒の太陽騎士の直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The knights of the ancient kingdom of Balder
wielded these rock-solid, long swords which
are excellent for thrust attacks.
Balder was the home of Knight King Rendal,
but the kingdom was reduced to ruins after
a widespread outbreak of Undead.
Name: 暗黒の刺突直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

This standard greatsword is normally wielded
with two hands due to its great weight.

Usually swung in large arcs and effective
against multiple foes. Far from ideal when
fighting in tight quarters.
Name: 暗黒のバスタードソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Axe
Attack type: Regular

Standard battle axe. Inflicts regular damage,
making it effective in various situations.
Powerful attack due to its weight, but one
wrong swing leaves the wielder wide open,
so timing and proximity to the enemy must
be judged carefully.
Name: 暗黒のバトルアクス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

The preferred black bow of the heroic
archer Pharis.

Has a longer range than standard bows,
but is more difficult to use. Without proper
abilities, results will be underwhelming.
Name: 暗黒のハンターの弓

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Metal hammer of Andre of Astora,
blacksmith at the Old Church.

Can be used as a strike weapon, but better
left in the hands of its talented owner.
Name: 暗黒のアンドレの金槌

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular

The wide blade of this straight sword
emphasizes slicing and has no thrust attack.

The horizontal sweeping motion makes this
sword effective against multiple enemies.
Name: 暗黒のブロードソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Axe
Attack type: Regular

Giant butcher knife wielded by the Undead
man-eating cook lurking in the Depths.
More a tool for subduing and preparing live
catches than an actual weapon. Those who
have faced this deadly blade have a deeper
sense of how helpless prey must feel.
Name: 暗黒の大包丁

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Fists
Attack type: Strike

The weapon augments one's bare hands
with thick, studded leather.

The Caestus has a short reach, but quick
cool down. Amount of damage inflicted is
dependent on its wearer's strength.
Name: 暗黒のセスタス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Fists
Attack type: Slash

A weapon formed by three sharp claws.

Attacks cause bleeding, and the wounds
inflicted are not easily mended. Preferred
weapon of the spooks of an Eastern land.
Name: 暗黒のかぎ爪

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

This larger type of greatsword is normally
wielded with two hands due to its weight.

This highly flexible greatsword can be used
to attack in swings or thrusts.
Name: 暗黒のクレイモア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

A simple wooden club.
This simple bladeless strike weapon is
effective against most foes, is easily
handled, and can break the guard of a shield.
However, a single miss makes one wide open,
so timing and proximities are crucial.
Name: 暗黒のクラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Composite bow emphasizing power.
Requires more strength than standard bows.

However, its range is shorter, making it
unfit for sniping.
Name: 暗黒のコンポジットボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

This standard small dagger has only a modest
attack but can be jabbed in rapid succession,
and is effective in critical hits such as
after a parry or when stabbing in the back.
With both slash and thrust attacks, this
dagger is useful in various situations.
Name: 暗黒のダガー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular

The sword of the knights of the Four Kings of
New Londo. Its blade is wide and thick, and
it is wielded in an unusual manner.
When the Four Kings were seduced by evil,
their knights became Darkwraiths, servants
of the Dark who wielded these darkswords.
Name: 暗黒のダークソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Ultra Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

The lesser Capra demons use these greatswords
in pairs. The blade is cast iron and hooked.

The sword is imbued with no particular magic,
but for those who have the strength, its
great weight will smash foes mercilessly.
Name: 暗黒のデーモンの鉈

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greataxe
Attack type: Regular

Carved from the bones of fellow demons.
Wielded by the lesser Taurus demons.

This axe is imbued with no special power,
but can merrily beat foes to a pulp,
providing you have the strength to wield it.
Name: 暗黒のデーモンの大斧

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The largest of the thrusting swords.
Can pierce an armored knight in one thrust.

The blade is also sharp,
allowing slicing as well.
Name: 暗黒のエストック

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Small curved sword. Each hit inflicts little
damage, but fluid chain attacks are deadly.

The falchion's sharp slashing attacks are
effective against cloth and flesh, but not
against metal armor or tough scales.
Name: 暗黒のファルシオン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

This greatsword with an undulating blade is
the choice weapon of the slithering serpent
men of Sen's Fortress.

This weapon is designed to flay the skin and
causes heavy bleeding.
Name: 暗黒のフランベルジェ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Axe
Attack type: Regular

Sliced tail of the gargoyle guarding the
Bell of Awakening in the Undead Church.

Can be used as a bronze battle axe.
Bends dramatically during large attacks,
owing to its nature as a tail.
Name: 暗黒のガーゴイルの尾斧

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Regular

Halberd of the gargoyle guarding the
Bell of Awakening in the Undead Church.

Perfectly standard bronze halberd
without any special power.
Name: 暗黒のガーゴイルの斧槍

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Great Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Giant tree branch serves as a wooden club.
Smashes enemies from upside the head.

The leaping attack is a trademark of clubs,
and this giant club is no exception.
Name: 暗黒のグレートクラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Slash

Weapon with a long curved blade. Converted
from a wheat-harvesting tool.

The magnificent sharp curved blade
instills fear in opponents. Perhaps it is
their survival instinct at work.
Name: 暗黒の鎌

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Greataxe
Attack type: Regular

This greataxe is a veritable mass of iron.
Its weight sends foes flying, but makes it
difficult to handle without inhuman strength.

Any miss makes one very vulnerable, as each
swing requires the full force of the body.
Name: 暗黒のグレートアクス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Ultra Greatsword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

One of the gigantic straight greatswords.

Very few have what it takes to wield this
incredibly heavy, damage-dealing monster.
A favorite of the Knights Berenike, known for
their heavy armor, and Black Iron Tarkus.
Name: 暗黒のグレートソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Long-hilted weapon mixing spear and axe is
difficult to handle, requiring both strength
and dexterity. The Halberd has two elementary
attacks: spear-like thrusting and large
sweeping swings. However, one false swing
and the wielder is left wide open.
Name: 暗黒のハルバード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Axe
Attack type: Regular

Small hand axe. Appears identical to a
lumberjack's tool, but has an ideal weight
and strength, and is easy to handle.
One wrong swing leaves the wielder wide
open, so timing and proximity to the enemy
must be judged carefully.
Name: 暗黒のハンドアクス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
The Katana is drawn from the scabbard at
lightning speed, using an Iaijutsu technique.

Iaijutsu allows the wielder to charge
forward to swiftly cut down distant foes.
Name: 暗黒の居合い刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash

This wide single-edged shortsword is
the favorite of lowly thieves and bandits.

Primarily a slicing weapon, but highly
effective when used for critical hits,
such as after parrying or from behind.
Name: 暗黒の短刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Great Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Large wooden club.

The giant Undead of Blighttown wield these
clubs, which became poisonous from the
influence of their surroundings.
Name: 暗黒の蛮兵クラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Large bow. Projectile weapon for experienced
hunters. Equip arrows to use.

Hold bow and press <?platmsg@10002?> to aim.
Aim for heads of humanoid foes.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of arrows.
Name: 暗黒のロングボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Widely-used standard straight sword, only
matched in ubiquity by the shortsword.

An accessible sword which inflicts consistent
regular damage and high slash damage, making
it applicable to a variety of situations.
Name: 暗黒のロングソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Thrust

Halberd with a large, hard beak-like
protrusion. Inflicts thrust damage.
Instead of thrusting like a spear, the
wielder of the Lucerne aims to club
the head with its hard beak.
Name: 暗黒のルッツエルン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Iron hammer with a protrusive pommel.
Standard weapon for clerics.
This simple bladeless strike weapon is
effective against most foes, and can
break the guard of a shield. However,
one miss leaves one wide open.
Name: 暗黒のメイス

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

Standard small thrusting sword.
Unsharpened but pointed solid
shaft can pierce tough armor.

Can be thrust using the weight of one's body,
and is very effective for critical attacks.
Name: 暗黒のメイル・ブレイカー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

Hammer with sharp spikes on its pommel.
One of the more barbaric cleric weapons.

The effect of these spikes makes this
strike-based weapon also cause bleeding.
Name: 暗黒のモーニングスター

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

Giant curved sword forged using special
methods in an Eastern land.
This unparalleled weapon cuts like a Katana
but is heavier than a Nata machete.
Requires extreme strength, dexterity,
and stamina to wield.
Name: 暗黒の大曲刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Whip
Attack type: Regular

Whip with sharp spikes.

Only slightly effective against armor and
tough scales, but quite formidable against
enemies with exposed skin.
Also causes heavy bleeding.
Name: 暗黒のスパイクウィップ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

This dagger is useful after parrying and is
normally equipped in the left hand.

A favorite of the knights of Carim, who are
famous for fighting without a shield.
Name: 暗黒のパリングダガー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Spear with blade attached to broad point.
Boasts long reach, and can slice.

The wide range of this spear makes it
adaptable to many situations. Its strength
lies in its length, but in cramped quarters,
this backfires, and slices ricochet off walls.
Name: 暗黒のパルチザン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Thrust

Traditionally a mining tool, but the hard
cone on the pommel is effective in battle.

A downward swing of the Pickaxe can crush
stone; a human head would be an afterthought.
Name: 暗黒のつるはし

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Long Spear
Attack type: Thrust

Long spear with a very long red hilt.
Traditionally used by groups of soldiers.
Specially designed for distance thrusting.
Has the longest range of the non-projectile
weapons, but its very length makes it
somewhat difficult to handle.
Name: 暗黒のパイク

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

Standard thrusting sword. Regular one-handed
attack can be delivered with shield held up.
Can parry with use of left hand.

Thrusting attacks pierce and are effective
against foes with hard exteriors, but the
wielder is left open to damage after a swing.
Name: 暗黒のレイピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Strike

A club with leather nailed to the pommel.
The burg Undead merchant proudly peddles
this club, but its reinforcement is shoddy.
Indeed, its attack is stronger, but the
club is no longer dependably sturdy.
Name: 暗黒の強化クラブ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Thrusting Sword
Attack type: Thrust

A rapier with intricate decorations. Chosen
weapon of the infamous Undead Prince Ricard.
Ricard's exploits are told in a monomyth.
He was born into royalty, but wandered the
lands in a fateful ill-conceived journey.
He became Undead, and disappeared up North.
Name: 暗黒の貴族の刺剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Small curved sword. Each hit inflicts little
damage, but fluid chain attacks are deadly.

The scimitar's sharp slashing attacks are
effective against cloth and flesh, but not
against metal armor or tough scales.
Name: 暗黒のシミター

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Halberd
Attack type: Slash

Halberd with a large blade.
Scythe adjusted for battle.

Designed especially for slicing. However,
one false swing leaves one wide open.
Name: 暗黒のサイズ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Greatsword
Attack type: Slash

A curved greatsword used in a
mysterious ancient rite.

Imbued with a frightful occult energy
which restores HP with each hit.
Name: 暗黒のラム・ダオ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Bow
Attack type: none

Small bow. Standard projectile weapon.
Equip arrows to use.

Hold bow and press <?platmsg@10002?> to aim.
Aim for heads of humanoid foes.
Press <?platmsg@10003?>/<?platmsg@10004?> to change type of arrows.
Name: 暗黒のショートボウ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

This small straight sword is widely used,
to an extent only matched by the longsword.

An accessible sword which inflicts consistent
regular damage and high slash damage, making
it applicable to a variety of situations.
Name: 暗黒のショートソード

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Curved sword with sharply curved blade.

Created by Arstor, Earl of Carim.
Requires great skill to wield, but evades
shield defense to sneak in damage.
Name: 暗黒のショーテル

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Thrust

Standard spear used commonly by soldiers.
Long reach, and can be used with shield up.
Effective against hard exteriors, and can hit
for high damage at the right moment of an
enemy's swing. But the hit radius is small,
and it is easily blocked by shields.
Name: 暗黒のショートスピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Straight Sword
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

The hilt of this lost sword was found
discarded in the Undead Asylum.

Only slightly better than one's bare hands,
and not recommended for extensive use.
Be certain to find a replacement quickly.
Name: 暗黒のすごく折れた直剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
Known for its brisk slashing motions.

The Uchigatana cuts beautifully and causes
bleeding, but its blade is easily nicked.
Name: 暗黒の打刀

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Thrust

Hammer with a large beak-shaped pommel.
Originally a pickaxe; redesigned for battle.

This simple but deadly weapon hits heavily
with thrust damage, such that it easily
cracks metal armor.
Name: 暗黒のウォーピック

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Katana
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

Katana forged in an Eastern land.
Very unusual specimen with a long blade.

The blade is extremely long,
but as a result, quite easily broken.
Name: 暗黒の名刀なんとか

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Whip
Attack type: Regular

Leather whip.
Not intended for battle.

Virtually ineffective against armor and tough
scales, but quite formidable against enemies
with exposed skin.
Name: 暗黒のウィップ

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Thrust

A long-hilted spear with a barbed point.
Long reach, and can be used with shield up.
Effective against hard exteriors, and hits
for high damage at the right moment of an
enemy's swing. But the hit radius is small,
and it is easily blocked by shields.
Name: 暗黒のロングスピア

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Ultra Greatsword
Attack type: Regular

One of the gigantic straight greatswords.

As the name suggests, the Zweihander is held
with two hands, but its wielder must still be
inhumanly strong. It is this great weight
that sends foes flying when hit solidly.
Name: 暗黒のツヴァイヘンダー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Catalyst
Attack type: Strike

Sorcery catalyst of lost land of Oolacile.
Formed by enchanted whitebark branches.

The whitebark boosts sorcery adjustment,
but the sorceries of this lost land are
gentle and not affected by intelligence.
Name: ウーラシールの白枝

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Curved Sword
Attack type: Slash

Curved sword of Anor Londo painting guards.
Unique shape with flat tip.
The guardians, who strike down those who
dare threaten the paintings, attack in a
continuous, circular dancing motion,
a technique passed down through generations.
Name: エレーミアスの曲剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash/Thrust

This dagger is useful after parrying and is
normally equipped in the left hand.

A favorite of the knights of Carim, who are
famous for fighting without a shield.
Name: パリングダガー

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Spear
Attack type: Regular/Thrust

Spear with blade attached to broad point.
Boasts long reach, and can slice.

The wide range of this spear makes it
adaptable to many situations. Its strength
lies in its length, but in cramped quarters,
this backfires, and slices ricochet off walls.
Name: パルチザン

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Hammer
Attack type: Thrust

Traditionally a mining tool, but the hard
cone on the pommel is effective in battle.

A downward swing of the Pickaxe can crush
stone; a human head would be an afterthought.
Name: つるはし

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Shield
Attack type: Thrust

Shield of certain knights of Catarina, used
in attacks with a large protrusion in center.

Can be used as a thrust weapon.
Name: ピアスシールド

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Long Spear
Attack type: Thrust

Long spear with a very long red hilt.
Traditionally used by groups of soldiers.
Specially designed for distance thrusting.
Has the longest range of the non-projectile
weapons, but its very length makes it
somewhat difficult to handle.
Name: パイク

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Small Shield
Attack type: Strike

Makeshift shield built from wood planks.
Provides minimal protection,
but at a cost of moderate humiliation.
Name: 木板の盾

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Arrow
Attack type: Thrust

Arrow with point dipped in poison.
Ensures the demise of prey in a hunt,
or the target in an assassination.
Once an enemy is poisoned, one need
only wait.
Name: 黒木の矢

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Dagger
Attack type: Slash

This sword, one of the rare dragon weapons,
came from the tail of Priscilla, the Dragon
Crossbreed in the painted world of Ariamis.
Possessing the power of lifehunt, it dances
about when wielded, in a fashion reminiscent
of the white-robed painting guardians.
Name: 半竜の短剣

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Pyromancy Flame
Attack type: Strike

Flame medium used by Great Swamp pyromancers.
Pyromancers arouse this flame to produce
various fire arts.
Equip pyromancer flame to produce pyromancy.
Attune pyromancies from a scroll at bonfire.
Most pyromancies have limited no. of uses.
Name: 呪術の火

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Pyromancy Flame
Attack type: Strike

Pyromancy flame drawing upon the latent power
of Quelana of Izalith, mother of pyromancy.
For the pyromancer, a flame is a precious
thing indeed, to be nurtured, often for an
entire lifetime. When the flame is shared, it
creates an eternal bond between the parties.
Name: 混沌の火＋１

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Pyromancy Flame
Attack type: Strike

Flame medium used by Great Swamp pyromancers.
Pyromancers arouse this flame to produce
various fire arts.
Equip pyromancer flame to produce pyromancy.
Attune pyromancies from a scroll at bonfire.
Most pyromancies have limited no. of uses.
Name: 呪術の火＋１

EnglishDescription:
Weapon type: Pyromancy Flame
Attack type: Strike

Pyromancy flame drawing upon the latent power
of Quelana of Izalith, mother of pyromancy.
